body:
*   Contrast helps readability

*   Also helps in Hierarchy

*   It guides attention without extra noise.


Overusing bright or saturated colors for body text reduces comfort and focus. Good typography uses color to guide the eye, not distract it.

```
:root {
  --bg: #0b0b0c;
  --text: #eaeaf0;
  --muted: #8b8b94;
  --accent: #ff6f61;
}
```

This is the most simple way of having contrast in a website, we have more detailed contrast Snippets in the Code Snippets app!
